{"tid":1659970,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"狙擊SE2, 三叔明年推平價高性能A91","createTime":"2019-10-17T08:42:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T16:56:49.000Z","uid":12628,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"f347fff7dda01f34f47a03d5533933a2e1ed2a17","tid":1659970,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T08:42:54.000Z","msg":"最近 iPhone SE2 被曝光將於明年第一季度發布之後，消費者的關注方向轉向了明年價格約 HK$3,200 的平價旗艦手機，這將是明年第一季度的一場大戰。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fdn.gsmarena.com/imgroot/news/19/10/samsung-galaxy-a91-leak/-1220x526/gsmarena_003.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffdn.gsmarena.com%2Fimgroot%2Fnews%2F19%2F10%2Fsamsung-galaxy-a91-leak%2F-1220x526%2Fgsmarena_003.jpg&h=eed370fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有傳聞，Samsung 在準備 Galaxy A91，來與 iPhone SE2 進行平價旗艦鬥爭。對於 Samsung Galaxy A91，很可能就是 Galaxy A90 5G 的 4G 版本。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">性能規格上，Galaxy A91 擁有 6.7吋 Full HD+ 解像度 Infinity-U 水滴屏幕，搭載 Snapdragon 855 處理器，配以 8GB RAM+128GB ROM。拍攝上，Galaxy A91 採用前置 3200萬像素鏡頭 F/2.2光圈，後置 4800萬像素 + 1200萬像素 + 500萬像素三鏡配置。除此之外，Galaxy A91 擁有 4500mAh，支援 45W 快速充電功能，運行 Android 10 系統等。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n有一些未經證實的報導稱，Galaxy A91可能會在今年年底之前在印度等國家發布。Galaxy A91 估計售價在 HK$4400 左右。"},{"pid":"7b49d5a436dc2cf072c8af0cb4766994bcc391c7","tid":1659970,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T08:42:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jwJzHzo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjwJzHzo.jpg&h=eb217258&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"aba71c6d604d27ed96260b67f3dbfa7dd58541ca","tid":1659970,"uid":12628,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T08:44:50.000Z","msg":"配置唔差喎，有快充 有大電，有s855, 8+128, 4000頭大廠機，有吸引力！"},{"pid":"3697f20e556b492613abd013d836e30365d62a3c","tid":1659970,"uid":4574,"like":21,"dislike":2,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T08:44: